          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-sm-8">
            <h2 class="heading">Shorten</h2>
            <p class="description">Short your long URL's to get a sleaky tiny URL which is  easy to remember and track. Zippy truncates your long links into clean short URL's so that you can share them on different social media platforms</p>
